---
title: Prompts vs Workflows vs Agents
---
mindmap
  root((LLM Systems))
    **Prompt**
      Single LLM call
      One input / one output
      No orchestration
      You control everything
    **Workflow**
      Multiple LLM calls
      Code controls flow
        Predetermined routing
        Defined steps
      Shared state
      Predictable
      Example
        Translate → Summarize → Format
    **Agent**
      LLM controls flow
        Picks tools dynamically
        Decides when to stop
      Unpredictable
      Example
        Fix this bug autonomously
    **Key Question**
      Who decides next step?
        Prompt → Developer
        Workflow → Code
        Agent → LLM
